content: This is a wonderful game. There are so many "coding" games out there now, but this one actually teaches some fundamentals of programming for kids. Our 4.5 and 6 year olds picked it up and had no problem. It's a bit too complicated for our 3 year old. It's also actually really fun for adults too. I don't play games, but I do actually enjoy helping the kids here when they get stuck.
This app is very fun for my 6 year old son and the coding is great and easy
